window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I thought it would be a triumphant return back to Earth, but the situation on my new home is dire. An old enemy thought long dead has returned, and he's building an army of bloodsuckers.</p> <p>We are the Offenders, the greatest superhero team in Caliber City. Every single member of my superteam holds a piece of my heart, and I won't let anyone harm them. Even if he's a legendary vampire who once brought my world to its knees.</p>"; 
